name: Cyber ​​exhibition - The Virgin
description: Second NFT in a series that the artist calls 'Cyber ​​exhibition'. Scenery created with 3D modeling technique and rendering around a physical piece in graphite in A3 format. "Cyber ​​Exposition" reflects the viewer's reactions around the virtual simulation environment, revealing familiarity with the almost android world of instantaneous feelings like optical fibers.
